{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1778975942690,"sessionID":"ses_1ccc56ae9ffe9yZL6R6jVJHLqB","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"call_aH8cp74AfOsjF8FuuUZTSHKM","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json","offset":1,"limit":2000},"output":"<path>/__w/eval-ont-agent-go/eval-ont-agent-go/__issue_context__.json</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: {\n2:   \"body\": \"\\n\\nTransferred from\\nhttps://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/22181\\n\\nPlease provide as much information as you can:\\n\\n* **GO term ID and Label**\\n* \\nGO:0061817    endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering\\nThe attachment of an endoplasmic reticulum membrane to the plasma membrane via molecular tethers.\\n\\n* **Reason for deprecation** Put an x in the appropriate box: \\n\\n - [x] The reason for obsoletion is that this term represents a molecular function.\\n\\n* **\\\"Replace by\\\" term (ID and label)**\\nIf all annotations can safely be moved to that term\\n\\n* **\\\"Consider\\\" term(s) (ID and label)**\\n\\nThis is an MF and should use\\n[GO:0160214]  endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane adaptor activity\\npart_of GO:0051643   endoplasmic reticulum localization\\n\\nGO:0061817    endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering\\ncould have direct replacemnt  GO:0051643   endoplasmic reticulum localization\\nbut curators should check that the correct MF term is annotated\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n* **Are there annotations to this term?**\\n- How many EXP: 15\\n\\n* **Are there mappings and cross references to this term? (InterPro, Keywords; check QuickGO cross-references section)**\\n\\n* **Is this term in a subset? (check the AmiGO page for that term)**\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\\n\\n----\\nChecklist for ontology editor\\n\\n***Check term usage and metadata in Protégé***\\n- [ ] check term usage in the ontology \\n- [ ] check internal mappings: RHEA, EC, MetaCyc\\n- [ ] check subset usage\\n- [ ] check taxon constraints \\n\\n***Check annotations***\\n- [ ] create Annotation Review spreadsheet \\n- * Annotation Review template: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1izV3q1jnq_Ybg5MJ53O_b5BCTkGtjl_Fi-cOg3-7eBE/edit#gid=0\\n- * Instructions: https://wiki.geneontology.org/Annotation_Review_Request\\n- [ ] create annotation review ticket: https://github.com/geneontology/go-annotation/issues/new?assignees=&labels=annotation+review&template=annotation-review-for-obsoletion.md&title=Revi... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n3:   \"comments\": [\n4:     {\n5:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBKemAA\",\n6:       \"author\": {\n7:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n8:       },\n9:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n10:       \"body\": \"The proposal has been made to obsolete GO:0061817 endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering.\\n\\n\\n* The reason for obsoletion is that this term represents a molecular function.\\n\\nExperimental annotations\\nCGD 4\\nPomBase 13 DONE\\nTAIR 2\\nUniProt 2 DONE\\n\\n8 InterPro2GO mappings have been removed.\\n\\nAnnotations can be viewed here: https://github.com/geneontology/go-annotation/issues/6383\\n\\nAnnotations can be transferred to\\nGO:0160214 endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane adaptor activity.\\n\\nAny comments can be  added to the issue:  https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31873\\n\\n\\nThanks, \",\n11:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-04T17:27:40Z\",\n12:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n13:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n14:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n15:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n16:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31873#issuecomment-4373063168\",\n17:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n18:     },\n19:     {\n20:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBKexOQ\",\n21:       \"author\": {\n22:         \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n23:       },\n24:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n25:       \"body\": \"@dragon-ai-agent please obsolete GO:0061817 endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering.\",\n26:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-04T17:28:08Z\",\n27:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n28:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n29:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n30:       \"reactionGroups\": [\n31:         {\n32:           \"content\": \"EYES\",\n33:           \"users\": {\n34:             \"totalCount\": 1\n35:           }\n36:         }\n37:       ],\n38:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31873#issuecomment-4373066041\",\n39:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n40:     },\n41:     {\n42:       \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBKe6mg\",\n43:       \"author\": {\n44:         \"login\": \"dragon-ai-agent\"\n45:       },\n46:       \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n47:       \"body\": \"🤖 Working on it...\\n\\nFollow along: [View workflow run](https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/actions/runs/25333221838)\\n\\n*— @dragon-ai-agent*\",\n48:       \"createdAt\": \"2026-05-04T17:28:31Z\",\n49:       \"includesCreatedEdit\": false,\n50:       \"isMinimized\": false,\n51:       \"minimizedReason\": \"\",\n52:       \"reactionGroups\": [],\n53:       \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31873#issuecomment-4373068442\",\n54:       \"viewerDidAuthor\": false\n55:     }\n56:   ],\n57:   \"title\": \"Obsoletion request: GO:0061817    endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering\",\n58:   \"url\": \"https://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/31873\"\n59: }\n\n(End of file - total 59 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"{\n  \"body\": \"\\n\\nTransferred from\\nhttps://github.com/geneontology/go-ontology/issues/22181\\n\\nPlease provide as much information as you can:\\n\\n* **GO term ID and Label**\\n* \\nGO:0061817    endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering\\nThe attachment of an endoplasmic reticulum membrane to the plasma membrane via molecular tethers.\\n\\n* **Reason for deprecation** Put an x in the appropriate box: \\n\\n - [x] The reason for obsoletion is that this term represents a molecular function.\\n\\n* **\\\"Replace by\\\" term (ID and label)**\\nIf all annotations can safely be moved to that term\\n\\n* **\\\"Consider\\\" term(s) (ID and label)**\\n\\nThis is an MF and should use\\n[GO:0160214]  endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane adaptor activity\\npart_of GO:0051643   endoplasmic reticulum localization\\n\\nGO:0061817    endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering\\ncould have direct replacemnt  GO:0051643   endoplasmic reticulum localization\\nbut curators should check that the correct MF term is annotated\\n\\n\\n\\n\\n* **Are there annotations to this term?**\\n- How many EXP: 15\\n\\n* **Are there mappings and cross references to this term? (InterPro, Keywords; check QuickGO cross-references section)**\\n\\n* **Is this term in a subset? (check the AmiGO page for that term)**\\n\\n* **Any other information**\\n\\n\\n----\\nChecklist for ontology editor\\n\\n***Check term usage and metadata in Protégé***\\n- [ ] check term usage in the ontology \\n- [ ] check internal mappings: RHEA, EC, MetaCyc\\n- [ ] check subset usage\\n- [ ] check taxon constraints \\n\\n***Check annotations***\\n- [ ] create Annotation Review spreadsheet \\n- * Annotation Review template: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1izV3q1jnq_Ybg5MJ53O_b5BCTkGtjl_Fi-cOg3-7eBE/edit#gid=0\\n- * Instructions: https://wiki.geneontology.org/Annotation_Review_Request\\n- [ ] create annotation review ticket: https://github.com/geneontology/go-annotation/issues/new?assignees=&labels=annotation+review&template=annotation-review-for-obsoletion.md&title=Revi... (line truncated to 2000 chars)\n  \"comments\": [\n    {\n      \"id\": \"IC_kwDOAkAHws8AAAABBKemAA\",\n      \"author\": {\n        \"login\": \"raymond91125\"\n      },\n      \"authorAssociation\": \"MEMBER\",\n      \"body\": \"The proposal has been made to obsolete GO:0061817 endoplasmic reticulum-plasma membrane tethering.\\n\\n\\n* T